    {
      "instruction": "<p>Melt 15g <span class=\"text-purple\">[25g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[30g]</span> <strong>butter</strong> in a pot over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once melted, add 20g<span class=\"text-purple\"> [30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1 min or until a sandy paste forms</p><p>Add 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [230ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>gradually and whisk for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>white sauce</strong></p>",
